00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:35,280
I said I would buy you a drink
when you get discharged.

262
00:18:35,610 --> 00:18:37,040
That sounds great.

263
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:39,610
It was so hard to stay away from alcohol.

264
00:18:40,050 --> 00:18:41,280
You just name it. It's my treat.

265
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:44,720
-I like your attitude today.
-Right?

266
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,360
Gosh, it hurts.

267
00:18:51,430 --> 00:18:53,630
-What's wrong? What hurts?
-Yes. My wound is hurting.

268
00:18:53,690 --> 00:18:55,300
-Your wound?
-It hurts.

269
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:58,470
Come here. Let's go.

270
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:07,110
-Soo-hyun.
-Yes?

271
00:19:07,170 --> 00:19:08,510
I thought you were hurt in the head.

272
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:10,140
-Shut it.
-Yes, ma'am.

273
00:19:14,010 --> 00:19:15,180
The drink is so smooth today.

274
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,820
Come on. Bottoms up.

275
00:19:25,090 --> 00:19:26,390
When will you tell me?

276
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,400
What?

277
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,300
Something is up. Something bad.

278
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,600
No. I just wanted to have a drink

279
00:19:32,670 --> 00:19:35,070
since you got discharged.

280
00:19:35,940 --> 00:19:37,040
Kim Ga-on.

281
00:19:44,010 --> 00:19:46,650
I just wanted to see you today.

282
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,950
I really should stick to that.

283
00:19:54,490 --> 00:19:57,060
Hey, how can that happen?
Is that even possible?

284
00:19:57,890 --> 00:19:59,730
I saw him with my own two eyes.

285
00:20:00,230 --> 00:20:03,460
I can never forget that jerk's face.

286
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:05,500
But how...

287
00:20:07,030 --> 00:20:09,940
A warden can't pull off
something like that.

288
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,870
Not even the head
of the Korea Correctional Service.

289
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:14,040
It has to be someone higher up,
much higher up.

290
00:20:14,410 --> 00:20:17,340
I know. That's what Kang Yo-han is saying.

291
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,510
Right.

292
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:22,720
It makes sense, but maybe...

293
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,120
It makes too much sense.

294
00:20:25,450 --> 00:20:26,850
When I investigate a case,

295
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:30,390
