when a story makes perfect sense.

296
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:32,960
What do you think
Kang Yo-han's intention could be?

297
00:20:33,690 --> 00:20:36,730
He knows so much about your past,

298
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:39,400
