he had prepared just for you.

300
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:46,810
What if...
I mean, hypothetically speaking.

301
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:48,810
What if

302
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:51,850
he's doing all this
with an ulterior motive?

303
00:20:52,910 --> 00:20:56,680
What if he's intentionally stirring you up
to drag you into this?

304
00:21:02,690 --> 00:21:03,690
You never disappoint.

305
00:21:05,490 --> 00:21:06,830
I'll look into it.

306
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:10,860
I'll find out who's behind all this.

307
00:21:12,230 --> 00:21:15,370
It'll become an official investigation
once you get involved.

308
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:18,310
But the thing is,
I don't trust any of your higher-ups.

309
00:21:18,370 --> 00:21:20,770
-But still...
-Just give me some time.

310
00:21:21,610 --> 00:21:23,580
I'll play along with Kang Yo-han

311
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:25,080
and try to find out more.

312
00:21:25,910 --> 00:21:26,910
Okay?

313
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:47,000
This must be really hard for you, Ga-on.

314
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:55,110
To be honest, I was quite taken aback

315
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,710
by the brazenness

316
00:21:58,210 --> 00:22:00,980
of those who are behind this,
even though I have no idea who they are.

317
00:22:01,650 --> 00:22:02,680
Brazenness?

318
00:22:03,020 --> 00:22:05,390
Whoever did this
isn't afraid of getting caught.

319
00:22:05,450 --> 00:22:07,960
The substitute looked
nothing like the real one.

320
00:22:09,690 --> 00:22:11,730
My mom and dad...

321
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:18,030
They passed away like that,

322
00:22:18,370 --> 00:22:20,530
but their one and only son

323
00:22:22,300 --> 00:22:24,340
doesn't even know what really happened.

324
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:28,910
I can't...

325
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:36,320
Goodness, what's with this music?

326
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:47,280
Sun-ah, you did great.

327
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:51,220
I love you.

328
00:25:00,230 --> 00:25:01,560
Are you that proud of yourself?

329
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:04,430
I sure am.

330
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:08,800
You know how hard I've had to work.

331
00:25:10,670 --> 00:25:14,670
To get out of that disgusting gutter
and come this far.

332
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:17,980
Right, I must give you props
for what you managed to pull today.

333
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:20,850
I'm truly impressed by you.

334
00:25:24,420 --> 00:25:25,590
You really think so?

335
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,800
You're right.

336
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:40,330
Jung Sun-ah is an impressive woman.

337
00:25:41,870 --> 00:25:43,840
Anyway, are you going somewhere?

338
00:25:45,470 --> 00:25:46,470
Yes.

339
00:25:48,310 --> 00:25:50,580
I should go see my Young Master.

340
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:01,050
[Today's news.]

341
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:02,720
[Crime Reporting Hotline]

342
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:04,060
