has announced a series of measures]

343
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:05,230
[Rigorous Law and Order Enforcement
for Safer Korea]

344
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:06,360
[to strengthen law and order.]

345
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:07,060
[Police]

346
00:26:06,430 --> 00:26:10,130
[Due to the irrefutable effectiveness
