347
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,970
Stop. Let me check your backpack.

348
00:26:12,030 --> 00:26:13,400
Stand still.

349
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:16,470
[Police]

350
00:26:14,130 --> 00:26:15,340
