-Hand it over.

351
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,470
I said, arms up.

352
00:26:17,100 --> 00:26:20,540
[Rigorous Law and Order Enforcement
for Safer Korea]

353
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,380
Things seem to be getting quite serious.

354
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:27,050
[Rigorous Law and Order Enforcement
for Safer Korea]

355
00:26:24,380 --> 00:26:27,050
