357
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:35,660
You're clearly too busy
carrying out your important task

358
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,220
to even notice anything.

359
00:26:38,190 --> 00:26:39,530
I guess I'm the only fool here.

360
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,290
Ms. Oh, that's...

361
00:26:41,360 --> 00:26:42,360
Forget it.

362
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:51,000
[Rigorous Law and Order Enforcement
for Safer Korea]

363
