will be revised]

364
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:53,910
[so the heavy sentences demonstrated
by the Live Court Department]

365
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,980
[Chief Judge Kang Yo-han]

366
00:26:53,970 --> 00:26:55,610
