and communications activities.]

370
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:03,780
[Chief Judge Kang Yo-han]

371
00:27:02,950 --> 00:27:03,950
Who is it?

372
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:11,190
Hi, Young Master.

373
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:14,030
[Chief Judge Kang Yo-han]

374
00:27:22,140 --> 00:27:23,340
Have you lost your mind?

375
00:27:24,140 --> 00:27:26,210
How dare you barge in here?

376
00:27:26,370 --> 00:27:27,740
It's a pleasure to meet you.

377
00:27:28,210 --> 00:27:31,140
I'm Jung Sun-ah, and I'll be leading
the Operations Support Task Force

378
00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:32,680
for the Live Court Department.

379
00:27:33,350 --> 00:27:36,280
I look forward to working closely
with you, Judge Kang Yo-han.

380
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:51,430
