without my involvement.

476
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:53,930
[Minister of Justice Cha Kyung-hee]

477
00:33:54,430 --> 00:33:56,430
Seo Jeong-hak died out of the blue.

478
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,900
