479
00:33:59,330 --> 00:34:01,700
Did you find out about
the gang they have arrested?

480
00:34:01,770 --> 00:34:05,000
The National Intelligence Service won't
share anything as it's their jurisdiction.

481
00:34:05,510 --> 00:34:07,440
Darn those pigs.

482
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:11,239
So they will only answer to the President.

483
00:34:15,949 --> 00:34:18,650
Don't we have a team that's looking into
Heo Joong-se's corruption?

484
00:34:19,350 --> 00:34:20,250
Yes, Ms. Cha.

485
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:22,219
I will need some of them
on a different task.

486
00:34:22,290 --> 00:34:23,860
Which task?

487
00:34:27,630 --> 00:34:31,060
The new chairman of Social
Responsibility Foundation, Jung Sun-ah.

488
00:34:32,900 --> 00:34:35,770
It looks like a sly fox has gotten

489
00:34:33,969 --> 00:34:35,739
[Minister of Justice Cha Kyung-hee]

490
00:34:36,139 --> 00:34:39,139
her claws into our silly President.

491
00:34:41,770 --> 00:34:44,710
[285 S 7511]

492
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,660
Let's talk over a cup of coffee.

493
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:01,190
Sure. Sounds good.

494
00:35:03,230 --> 00:35:04,300
Elijah.

495
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:21,380
