817
00:53:46,120 --> 00:53:47,250
Nice to meet you.

818
00:53:47,590 --> 00:53:48,620
I'm a fan.

819
00:53:48,690 --> 00:53:49,990
I even signed up at your fan club.

820
00:53:58,030 --> 00:53:59,830
[Hello, Your Honor.]

821
00:53:59,930 --> 00:54:01,570
[I'm a huge fan.]

822
00:54:01,930 --> 00:54:03,200
You're so cool.

823
00:54:03,270 --> 00:54:05,100
[He's a psycho.]

824
