827
00:54:25,890 --> 00:54:27,160
Can I accept this?

828
00:54:28,260 --> 00:54:29,290
Good job.

829
00:54:30,800 --> 00:54:31,860
Thanks.

830
00:54:51,250 --> 00:54:54,220
So everything we've been doing was a show?

831
00:54:54,750 --> 00:54:55,850
A show?

832
00:54:58,420 --> 00:55:00,690
I don't care if you criticize me.

833
00:55:01,030 --> 00:55:04,000
But you can't invalidate our trials.

834
00:55:04,660 --> 00:55:08,330
If you do, you will be insulting
everyone who mustered up their courage.

835
00:55:09,070 --> 00:55:11,700
We just helped them get the ball rolling.

836
00:55:11,870 --> 00:55:14,570
We wouldn't have been able to get
anything done without their bravery.

837
00:55:16,910 --> 00:55:18,540
Sorry. I'm late.

838
00:55:18,610 --> 00:55:20,080
-Hello.
-Hey.

839
00:55:21,380 --> 00:55:22,450
Thank you.

840
00:55:23,750 --> 00:55:26,990
Nice to meet you. I'm Cho Min-sung
