842
00:55:29,490 --> 00:55:31,460
[Hardworking Police]

843
00:55:31,360 --> 00:55:32,520
[He was annoyed from the get-go.]

844
00:55:32,590 --> 00:55:35,460
[Is he the one who completely went berserk
