845
00:55:35,830 --> 00:55:36,930
[Yes.]

846
00:55:38,400 --> 00:55:40,200
You're Soo-hyun's team leader.

847
00:55:40,570 --> 00:55:44,140
Yes. Soo-hyun may seem too feminine
for the job, but she's a good cop.

848
00:55:44,540 --> 00:55:46,740
Sometimes, she's too eager. That's all.

849
00:55:47,240 --> 00:55:49,740
