Money is indeed a strong motive.

852
00:55:56,250 --> 00:55:57,180
For everyone.

853
00:55:57,250 --> 00:55:59,880
Mr. Kim, stop thinking
you have us figured out.

854
00:56:00,120 --> 00:56:01,690
Did I say something wrong?

855
00:56:01,820 --> 00:56:05,020
Do you know why I'm helping Mr. Kang?

856
00:56:06,830 --> 00:56:07,930
Why?

857
