897
00:58:56,290 --> 00:58:58,830
Okay. It won't be easy though.

898
00:58:59,430 --> 00:59:02,230
Don't hesitate to let me know
if there's anything I can help with.

899
00:59:02,300 --> 00:59:03,940
I really want to help.

900
00:59:07,410 --> 00:59:08,510
How pretty.

901
00:59:10,140 --> 00:59:13,310
A smile like that is exactly
what the public needs now.

902
00:59:13,580 --> 00:59:16,110
