1001
01:05:48,710 --> 01:05:49,710
Let's go!

1002
01:05:49,770 --> 01:05:54,880
My fellow patriots!
Tonight, we'll become the real heroes.

1003
01:05:54,980 --> 01:05:58,050
We'll take back our country. How?
Like this!

1004
01:05:58,120 --> 01:06:00,990
[We must put a stop to this madness.]

1005
01:06:02,120 --> 01:06:04,420
[Anger is contagious.]

1006
