had done their jobs properly.

1037
01:07:59,840 --> 01:08:00,840
So...

1038
01:08:04,440 --> 01:08:05,940
Have you made up your mind?

1039
01:08:06,480 --> 01:08:08,210
You were the one

1040
01:08:10,150 --> 01:08:11,380
