[I want my unpaid wages.]

1052
01:09:54,990 --> 01:09:56,050
Film me.

1053
01:10:04,260 --> 01:10:06,200
Go ahead and shoot me if you want!

1054
01:10:06,560 --> 01:10:09,300
How can a police officer aim a gun

1055
01:10:09,370 --> 01:10:11,140
at the heart of an unarmed civilian?

1056
01:10:11,200 --> 01:10:12,570
Aren't you ashamed to do this?

1057
01:10:25,120 --> 01:10:26,150
Do you regret it?

1058
01:10:32,420 --> 01:10:33,790
I can promise you this one thing.

1059
01:10:35,860 --> 01:10:37,460
The man who conned your parents

1060
01:10:38,330 --> 01:10:40,970
and the people who smuggled him away.

1061
01:10:42,670 --> 01:10:44,270
I'll make them pay for it.

1062
01:10:45,300 --> 01:10:46,600
As cruelly as possible.

1063
01:10:49,010 --> 01:10:50,540
It's not just about revenge.

1064
01:10:51,180 --> 01:10:52,280
Then what is it?

1065
01:10:54,650 --> 01:10:56,050
I want to fight this corrupt world

1066
01:10:56,610 --> 01:10:57,950
and right the wrong.

1067
01:11:10,960 --> 01:11:13,260
[The Devil Judge]

1068
01:11:13,330 --> 01:11:15,500
[Special thanks to Park Hyung-su
for his guest appearance.]

1069
01:11:43,930 --> 01:11:46,700
[Not people like Heo Joong-se
or Cha Kyung-hee.]

1070
01:11:46,830 --> 01:11:49,000
You should take over this country,
Young Master.

1071
01:11:49,100 --> 01:11:50,470
Become a shepherd dog?

1072
01:11:50,530 --> 01:11:51,640
[Let's do this.]

1073
01:11:51,700 --> 01:11:53,170
She plans to use us.

1074
01:11:53,240 --> 01:11:54,440
[It's time]

1075
01:11:54,770 --> 01:11:55,970
[to go after your sworn enemy]

1076
01:11:56,170 --> 01:11:58,180
[and those who smuggled him out.]

1077
01:11:58,280 --> 01:12:00,680
[I'll put together a much more loyal team]

1078
01:12:00,740 --> 01:12:02,480
and make sure they get the job done.

1079
01:12:02,080 --> 01:12:02,680
[Chairman Jung Sun-ah]

1080
01:12:03,180 --> 01:12:04,950
[Do you know how I feel right now?]

1081
01:12:05,020 --> 01:12:06,720
-Let go!
[-Is this none of your business?]

1082
01:12:06,780 --> 01:12:08,550
[You only care about your hunt.]

1083
01:12:08,650 --> 01:12:09,790
[If you want revenge, get it.]

1084
01:12:10,490 --> 01:12:11,620
[Don't hesitate.]

1085
01:12:12,390 --> 01:12:13,590
[Die!]


